Question Text: Derived variable for the time from sign-in to completion of SSN as SrvSS_SSNTime_v1r0 -RcrtSI_SignTime_v1r0 or SrvSS_SSN4dTime_v1r0 - RcrtSI_SignTime_v1r0 if partial SSN given.
Variable Label: Time from account to social security
Derivation Notes: Can be further derived to other time units (e.g. hours + fractions of hours) or as multiple time variables (e.g. hours, minutes, and seconds)
